  allow captain to enter the league
  show a grid of the available players
  allow captain to filter by position
  allow captain to search for players
  allow captain to view only undrafted players
  allow captain to watch players
  allow captain to view roster of any team
  allow captain to set auto draft mode
  allow captain to draft from a desktop/tablet/phone
  
